{"tid":1850844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［曬命區］邊個屋企好多口罩？","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:03:10.000Z","uid":242050,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d47dd2d8a04237977a64341470a9cbaebe124f","tid":1850844,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phR1oiC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphR1oiC.png&h=d826fbf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔係叫你入黎曬命啊</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每個人有足夠數量就可以，如果整個社區入面有人中招無戴口罩，你有一萬個口罩都唔等於你100%無事。所以如果你地有口罩而數量係多，不妨原價放售比附近嘅鄰居。"},{"pid":"27d756930f8ab85363797e61b966bc17631bcff0","tid":1850844,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:50:47.000Z","msg":"醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"526295ae3673cb296a2cf704d8091c8a4c5c9623","tid":1850844,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:51:12.000Z","msg":"就黎無口罩 用住底褲頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fefb7423d33bf05e29a3c4f357f7941b5fc1977","tid":1850844,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"剩3X個聽日唔排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c43cb1a373f694226695d651268535791007cc","tid":1850844,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"返工帶緊個 放工可唔可以帶返個個 堅係就冇口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點保存好"},{"pid":"dd4dd1cbc265827fa9bf9289339693da108be887","t